              "id": "IC_kwDOFcwZ1c6b4un5",
              "body": "### PR summary [332aa9fcfb](https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/21122/commits/332aa9fcfb3603c7b0fff63dd9ccb0f67d225f67)\n\n#### Import changes for modified files\n\nNo significant changes to the import graph\n\n\n<details><summary>Import changes for all files</summary>\n\n|Files|Import difference|\n|-|-|\n\n</details>\n\n---\n\n<details><summary>\n\n#### Declarations diff\n\n</summary>\n\n`+ RootPositiveForm`\n`+ RootPositiveForm.algebraMap_apply_eq_form_iff`\n`+ RootPositiveForm.algebraMap_formIn`\n`+ RootPositiveForm.formIn`\n`+ RootPositiveForm.form_apply_root_ne_zero`\n`+ RootPositiveForm.isSymm_formIn`\n`+ RootPositiveForm.zero_lt_formIn_apply_root`\n`+ RootPositiveForm.zero_lt_formIn_iff`\n`+ coroot'_apply_apply_mem_of_mem_span`\n`+ coxeterWeightIn_mem_set_of_isCrystallographic`\n`+ eq_restrictScalarsRange_iff`\n`+ four_nsmul_coPolarization_compl_polarization_apply_root`\n`+ isAnisotropic_of_isValuedIn`\n`+ pairingIn_same`\n`+ root'_apply_apply_mem_of_mem_span`\n`+ rootFormRP`\n`+ rootForm_self_non_neg'`\n`+ zero_lt_apply_root_root_iff'`\n`- IsRootPositive`\n`- instIsRootPositiveRootForm`\n`- instance : P.IsValuedIn R`\n`- rootForm_root_self_pos`\n<details>\n  <summary>You can run this locally as follows</summary>\n\n\n```bash\n## summary with just the declaration names:\n./scripts/declarations_diff.sh <optional_commit>\n\n## more verbose report:\n./scripts/declarations_diff.sh long <optional_commit>\n```\n</details>\n\nThe doc-module for `script/declarations_diff.sh` contains some details about this script.\n\n</details>\n\n---\n\n<details><summary>No changes to technical debt.</summary>\n\nYou can run this locally as\n```\n./scripts/technical-debt-metrics.sh pr_summary\n```\n* The `relative` value is the weighted *sum* of the differences with weight given by the *inverse* of the current value of the statistic.\n* The `absolute` value is the `relative` value divided by the total sum of the inverses of the current values (i.e. the weighted *average* of the differences).\n</details>\n",
